snippet.title: Fractal Youniverse
snippet.description:
We at Fractal Youniverse aim to produce incredible visual and audio content, both original and repackaged for purposes of education, inspiration and motivation. Our projects include many different platforms such as video montages, personal interviews, documentary films, asking people questions on the street, presenting my academic research and much more.  

Explore Your Youniverse,

David Patrick Harry
(Owner & Director)

PayPal: https://www.paypal.me/dpharry
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/fractalyouniverse

Website: http://www.davidpatrickharry.com
